hvirtual (1:1.1.5-2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Rebuilt for fix the libvorbis0a dependency
  * Removed the "lib" prefix on plugins
  * added nasm in the Build-Depends
  * Fixed the "linking shared library and static libraries" issue
  * Now building non-PIC code since it prevents some assembly to build
  (particularly in libavcodec)
  * libguicast now links to Xv, not Xv_pic
  * Moved the fourier code into a single library

