hvirtual (1:1.1.5-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream version
  * Quicktime: now, we use ffmpeg from the cinelerra source tree
  (marillat's version is too new)
  * Versioning: changed all version to Cinelerra version
  * Cleaned choice system of mmx/non-mmx sources
  (now using automake conditionals). mmx sources are no
  longer built when it is not needed.

