hvirtual (1.1.0-3) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fixed dependency problem (Bug reported by vizard on sourceforge)
  * Since avifile support is broken, it is disabled by default
  * Avifile was the only library in C++, we can now build with gcc 3.2
  * Upgraded libsndfile to the 0.0.28 version (newest version in unstable)
  * Since we build with gcc 3.2, enabled -mmmx

